parameters:
Flames flicker from the gaping hole... It seems to be an
artificial bonfire using underground gas.

...Perhaps there is simply no way to extinguish the flames.
Laura and the others' HP and MP have been fully restored.

Tch! Who the hell are you guys?! ...Huh? Two girls...?
What... Willing to be sold or something?

Heheh...! This one's good!! If I can sell all 'three' of
them, I can live a comfortable life for a while!
Hahaha! The meal ticket is talking back, huh?!
Fine... I don't mind sassy girls. I'll keep you as my slave!

Yeah, with this, we've secured our safety. Let's finish this
quickly. \SE[0]\SM[nod]

\SE[14]Ah, you scoundrel!! This hero Ryan will be your
opponent!! \SE[12]\SM[pop]Witness the blade of justice!

Damn, what a bunch of terrible people!! I won't let them
have their way...!!
N-No, Ryan...! It's dangerous, so please hide.

Please, Lunaroa. Let me fight with you...? I will protect
Ryan...!
I can't refuse if you make that kind of face...
...I understand. Please be careful. I believe in you, Laura.
人さらいは端っこでのびてる。
レベッカは意識を取り戻してる。
Thank you, Ryan... You saved me.

N-No, I was completely reliant on Laura and the others... I
didn't do anything significant at all...
That's not true! Ryan, you were amazing, right?

That's right. I don't know what would have happened if there
hadn't been any help.

Ryan... I was so happy. Thank you for coming to help me...
You really were like a hero...
レベッカ、ライアンの目の前に接近

When we get back... I'll give you lots and lots... of
rewards ♡ Will that be okay... ♡?
ラウラたちに視線移動
Oh my, kids these days are quite advanced...

Is that so? Didn't Laura propose to me when we were around
that age?

Huh...!? No... um... That was definitely just a moment of
being carried away... or rather, you could say it was
youthful indiscretion...
Was it all just a game to you... with me?

...Hawaa!! No, that's not it! I mean, even when I'm serious,
I'm serious!! Um...!
You are always my number one...!

Oh my... I've been told something nice. I understand. I just
couldn't help but want to see Laura being all flustered...

I'm sorry? ...But Laura, your movements earlier were really
good, you know? Rebecca-chan didn't get hurt, and Ryan-kun
too...

Lunaroa is just amazing... I-I'm nothing special... I'm
small and insignificant...!

Don't belittle yourself. It's okay. You're gradually
becoming stronger.

I, who have been watching you all this time, am saying it.
Don't worry. There is no mistake.

Besides... since I'm praising you, you should just be happy
about it... understood?
ルナロア。ラウラのそばに

When you come back, I'll give you lots and lots... of
rewards...♡, okay?
ルナロアドットで、ふきだしかなにかで…笑える？

I-I'm sorry... I couldn't help it because I was looking at
you with so much envy...
Uuu... My pure maiden's heart... is being toyed with...
Shall we go soon? We need to return those girls safely too.
ルナロア下へ。画面から消える・
C-Can I really receive the rewards as promised...!?
ラウラ追うようにダッシュ。で終わり。
編成にレベッカも追加。
強くはないけど、ライアンよりは一回り強い
Hello. Are you a human? Do you have any business?
I will warp you to the entrance of the mine.

There's a Unique Boss on the lower floor... Hmm... I wonder
what should we do about this...

It might be a bit of a spoiler, but... Do you still want to
hear it?
I still want to hear it

Oh... Am I going to tell you that...? Well, I guess I have
no choice...

If the Unique Boss is too strong, maybe it would be better
to defeat the Story Boss first. I don't want you to ask why
though.
Right. Let's pretend you didn't hear anything.

Tch! Who the hell are you guys?! ...Huh? Two girls...? Are
you... willing to be sold?

Hehehe...! This one is good!! If I can sell all 'three of
them', I can live a life of leisure for a while!
Hahaha! The meal ticket is talking back, huh?!

Alright... I don't mind feisty girls. \!I'll keep you as my
slave!

\SE[2] (Can I create an opening... Laura, can you cover for
me?)
ルナロア右へ、ラウラは左で挟み撃ちな形に

...What? Are you really planning to steal this one from me?
\!...Hahaha! This one is good!
ここで勇者ライアンくん下から登場

\SE[14]Ah, you scoundrel!! \!This hero Ryan will be your
opponent!!
ルナロア右からタックル。
飛ばされたレベッカをラウラが受け止める
\SE[16]Shall we clean up... Are you prepared?
Damn it!! You think I'll let you have it your way!!

\SM[jump]\SE[14]Oh, I'll fight too! \!You scoundrel!!
Prepare to face the blade of justice!!
ライアン参戦で戦闘開始。
大仰な技名が色々ある。まぁ弱いめで。
